me.timothy.tests.database

Class AdminUpdateMappingTest

  • java.lang.Object
    • me.timothy.tests.database.AdminUpdateMappingTest
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    MysqlAdminUpdateMappingTest

    public class AdminUpdateMappingTest
extends java.lang.Object
    Describes tests focused on testing an AdminUpdateMapping inside a MappingDatabase. The database should be completely empty before each test. The database will be modified. This should not be run against a production database.

      • testSave

        public void testSave()

        Tests the ability to save AdminUpdates

        This is a basic test to make sure that doing a standard save on an AdminUpdate does not result in any errors, and sets the id of the AdminUpdate to a positive integer, and the very same (using equals) AdminUpdate is returned using fetchAll

        This has the side-effect of checking AdminUpdates equals function is implemented.
